  <h2>How a Cash Sale Can Stop Foreclosure</h2>
  <p>When you're facing foreclosure, time is your most critical resource. Every day that passes narrows your options. Selling to a local cash buyer is often the fastest, cleanest way to move forward — before the bank takes action that damages your credit for years.</p>

  <div class="feature-grid">
